54.000Z","msg":"百二萬都唔夠<br />\n寮屋本身直頭unauthorised 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實好on9，班環保撚日日都話想過d鄉村生活，想住返係原地，好離地成件事<br />\n<br />\n出面成百萬香港人日日挨貴租貴樓住到大西北每日頻頻撲撲返工放工<br />\n你一個人嘅鄉村生活個塊地，可以幫到幾十個家庭住得好d，畀人收左收百二萬都叫天叫地好似好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大佬你咁多年慳埋慳埋咁多租金都值啦下話"},{"pid":"b52af12f49ce14e7f763d258d60fd606b999f096","tid":2265100,"uid":149908,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"你地唔係住果到，咁緊係咁講"},{"pid":"5039c58f0cde7a00eee7da8f2a43c8b04627f5cf","tid":2265100,"uid":165136,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9d32ab88be69cf4f6603d74d9e173834fc357ac4","tid":2265100,"uid":170249,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:21:23.000Z","msg":"拆樓補錢先賠得120萬咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n低啦你班原居民咁鐘意奶共 割鳩你老母臭韭黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:37:54.000Z","msg":"應該唔係原居民<br />\n原居民嗰啲點會輪到朱凱迪出嚟<br />\n鄉黑勾結嗰啲大家知邊啲議員啦<br />\n原居民啲村政府都依家都唔敢郁<br />\n欺善怕惡，搞就搞班無勢力嘅"},{"pid":"504224440d5a30a36470611b34ce3dff4c8e00ed","tid":2265100,"uid":301952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"80917e83b202c2bc9de32f98f64b8edc7afd11e2","tid":2265100,"uid":103325,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:56:51.000Z","msg":"你塊地都係霸返嚟嘅啫，而家有錢落袋仲想點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:41:12.000Z","msg":"好多仲要非法轉租<br />\n租左比雙非個啲乞衣<br />\n上水天平山村大把蝗話校服童住寮屋<br />\n而家淨係夠7年就送120萬比佢"},{"pid":"ff55f291b16b62f99bf264ffeede60d00f472d9d","tid":2265100,"uid":301952,"like